,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T00:52:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T00:56:52.000Z","msg":"要有爆炸性消息<br />\n規模要好似雷曼爆咁<br />\n<br />\n但你見習種連電影業啲錢都要收就知都唔少野"},{"pid":"9b1eb29c22e9e90765cf98dfa122695cc2bc4192","tid":783390,"uid":37502,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c66c1e8220080cd2718de433acdba096ae80bb91","tid":783390,"uid":128417,"like":191,"dislike":2,"score":189,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T13:35:06.000Z","msg":"班專家又鳩up  係度造謠生事<br />\n贏國記住要企硬  打低老美<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T00:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/215045_81dd6f3919ff46686e4fc8b248edd364.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F215045_81dd6f3919ff46686e4fc8b248edd364.png&h=8cb2f71d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3848a29b81b2c678284847336dd4b49c0762d60e","tid":783390,"uid":39855,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T00:59:44.000Z","msg":"貿易戰係以年，而且獨裁國家唔會認輸，你睇下委內瑞拉，伊朗。"},{"pid":"db7c7eb2b811be0d9b6e8fc8f98f75563ecb4123","tid":783390,"uid":39840,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T01:04:04.000Z","msg":"賀江兵@LaodouniM<br />\n<br />\n 11 時間11 時間前<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我現在很恐懼，我從來沒說過中國經濟兩個月內崩潰，從沒預測過中國黨那一年死。我上週接受《蘋果日報》小記者的時候強內容，之一不是很重要嗎？我認同蘋果大部分，因為採訪的時候聲音的確挺差，我沒說&ldquo;核心&rdquo;。除此之外，我希望海外媒i以蘋果日報為準。謝謝各位。 🙏對我造成的不便，你他媽的也不會問我"},{"pid":"3c5852d6cccb5a1de9a75cb48afca13adc69eaaa","tid":783390,"uid":86841,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T01:05:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf2fa6fc0f4eccd1041a44512e2a62cf8825d41f","tid":783390,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T01:06:39.000Z","msg":"驚閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eadf142a3b8313dedb150999a1ce87d67df06e9","tid":783390,"uid":32722,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T01:06:47.000Z","msg":"條友講得啱，可能中國錯判形勢，以為貿易戰只係打嘴炮<br />\n如果唔係就未必會加大豆等既關稅<br />\n呢類民生用品好易刺激通脹<br />\nCPI 一高 GDP 一跌，就會形成央行大敵 》 滯脹<br />\n而家再玩落去就係有咁既機會<br />\n然後配合順差下跌，人民幣有貶值壓力<br />\n但加息等於送債務問題歸天<br />\n我諗你掘番凱恩斯條屍出黎都拆唔掂"},{"pid":"2a7dd38102184afd7a629a1e9b6028f5c04da31b","tid":783390,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T01:10:44.000Z","msg":"專家食屎啦<br />\n<br />\n中國又成最後贏家"},{"pid":"2105ff82ee5fc8f3483722b45ec19420b9d7e095","tid":783390,"uid":132038,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T01:11:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b98a958d29e9537371bce6c2c4376884c9f8f6e3","tid":783390,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T01:18:37.000Z","msg":"開放金融市場啦<br />\n<br />\n無得玩架喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想賺錢就預埋班鬼佬"},{"pid":"ede0247b758d5e3e12114badb69180b798f2c14e","tid":783390,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T01:22:12.000Z","msg":"打飛機文"},{"pid":"c9d3ca26fffef73aecabb9bbad4cd4fd63048ebb","tid":783390,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T01:28:07.000Z","msg":"幾個月之前我老母仲諗住將啲美金換人仔，好彩叫佢唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7311e1e0dd53d87726f0485fb8263f79a4c112","tid":783390,"uid":7961,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T01:29:38.000Z","msg":"煩過支爆"},{"pid":"b7f0011af0477920639b484dd4d2427ce60915e2","tid":783390,"uid":1633,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T01:50:22.000Z","msg":"依靠高房價政策等於吸毒，初初食好high, 越食越多， 最後服毒過量...救都救唔翻了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0aad681f5814b1ac1e3a65bd46507585164589c","tid":783390,"uid":55194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T01:58:24.000Z","msg":"等睇人跳樓等左好耐，快"},{"pid":